  <string name="bd_bt_connect_fail_dialog_message">Bu brayl ekani yoqilganini va yaqin-atrofda ekanini tekshiring.\n\nAgar baribir ulanmasa, nosozlikni tuzatishga oid boshqa takliflar uchun “Batafsil” tugmasini ikki marta bosing.</string>
